    "title": "Assistant Store Manager - Forever 21 India - 2025 Hiring Drive",
    "description": "Grow your career with Forever 21 India! We are hiring a Assistant Store Manager for our Aurangabad team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Forever 21 India:\nForever 21 India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct regular stock audits and prevent pilferage\n• Train and motivate the sales team to deliver excellent service\n• Manage store operations to ensure smooth daily functioning\n• Assist in recruiting, onboarding, and performance management of staff\n• Maintain high standards of store hygiene and cleanliness\n• Achieve sales targets and improve store performance metrics\n• Coordinate with the supply chain team for timely stock delivery\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Inventory Management\n• Proficiency in POS Systems\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in Team Leadership\n• Proficiency in Omnichannel Retail\n• Proficiency in SAP Retail\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in E-commerce Integration\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Referral bonus program\n• Learning & development budget\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Aurangabad, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Forever 21 India!",
